# shadcn/ui primitives — scaffolded by the shadcn CLI. We treat these as
# third-party code even though they live in our tree, because shadcn's
# recommended workflow is to re-run the CLI and overwrite them when upstream
# updates. Running our lint rules on them (especially react-refresh's
# only-export-components) fights patterns shadcn deliberately uses.
src/components/ui/**
